    <h2>{`Creating the proxy`}</h2>
    <p>{`In fact, the proxy will be generated by the Entity Framework (in runtime). To be more accurate, each of the POCO classes have a proxy. This proxy will derive from your POCO classes. This will let the Entity Framework keeping track of the state change and enable the use of lazy loading. Since the proxy class derive from POCO classes, these one must not be sealed, private or abstract.`}</p>
